<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.2.9">
<l>puraṅkaḷ mūṉṟumōr māttiraip pōtil poṅke rikkirai kaṇṭava ṉampiṉ</l>
<l>caraṅka ḷēkoṭi tāyaṭu kiṉṟa cāmpa vāṉuṭaṉ niṟka<supplied>t</supplied>to  ḻutōm</l>
<l>iraṅku nīyemak kentaipi rāṉē yilaṅku veṅkati rōṉṟaṉci ṟuvā</l>
<l>kuraṅku kaṭkara cēvemmaik kollēl kūṟi ṉōmtaṭam poṅkattam poṅkō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We pray as we stand with Jāmbavat who is being destroyed</l>
<l rend="indent">by arrows as cruel as the bolts</l>
<l>Of the one who saw the three cities [of Trīpura become] fuel</l>
<l rend="indent">for a raging fire in a split second;</l>
<l>“Have pity for us, lord our father, child of the shining, hot rayed [sun],</l>
<l>King to the monkeys, don’t slay us,” we cry out.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, it’s a turbulent road; it’s a turbulent path!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
